# animate-color-font-desktop
Animasi warna huruf atau warna background seperti aplikasi Instagram

<style>
  .site-title {
    /* color: #f35626; */
    background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(92deg,#f35626,#feab3a);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    -webkit-animation: hue 60s infinite linear;
      font-family: 'open sans';
      font-size: 50px;
      font-weight: lighter;
  }
    
  .modif {
    color: #735626;
    background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(2deg,#f35626,#2eab3a);
    -webkit-background-clip: text; /* Hapus untuk background */
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    -webkit-animation: hue 10s infinite linear;
      font-family: 'open sans';
      font-size: 50px;
      font-weight: lighter;
  }    

@-webkit-keyframes hue {
  from {
    -webkit-filter: hue-rotate(0deg);
  }
  to {
    -webkit-filter: hue-rotate(-360deg);
  }
}
</style>

<body>
<h1 class="site-title">Animate.css</h1>
<h1 class="modif">Modification</h1>
</body>
